snippet.title: Vinemon: Sauce Edition - Eevee Expo 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's our Trailer that was part of @EeveeExpo's Eevee Expo 2!
We recommend you watch the full expo as many talented devs are featured alongside us!
https://youtu.be/7Y8YMWrpcsY

You can also follow their Twitter for future Expo announcements: 
https://twitter.com/EeveeExpo

You should also follow our Twitter for more updates on Vinemon:
https://twitter.com/SwoneVial

Join our Discord:
https://discord.gg/ZPpe8Fc

As well as check out our forum pages:
https://reliccastle.com/threads/6217/
https://www.pokecommunity.com/showthread.php?p=10609872#post10609872
